      ],
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Goal\n\n**Purpose**: Strategic or local outcome that orients the entire plan. Answers \"what success looks like.\"\n\n**Different from Task**: Goal = why + measurable outcome; Task = atomic executable action for Codex.\n\n**Canonical data shape**:\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"string\",\n  \"markdown\": \"string\",\n  \"priority\": \"critical|high|medium|low\",\n  \"status\": \"open|in-progress|achieved|blocked\",\n  \"successMetrics\": [\"string\", \"...\"] or nodeRef[],\n  \"owner\": \"string?\",\n  \"targetDate\": \"YYYY-MM-DD?\",\n  \"children\": [nodeRef]\n}\n```\n\n**Relationship rules**: Goals parent Tasks/Decisions/Constraints. Multiple Tasks roll up to one Goal. Full hierarchy support.",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
