      ],
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Constraint\n\n**Purpose**: Immutable boundary or requirement that Codex must respect.\n\n**Hard vs guidance**: Hard = must-fail validation; guidance = should-flag.\n\n**Typed categories**: schema, ux, performance, policy, resource, security.\n\n**Scope**: global (root-level) or subgraph (attached to Goal/Task).\n\n**Canonical data shape**:\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"string\",\n  \"markdown\": \"string\",\n  \"type\": \"schema|ux|performance|policy|...\",\n  \"severity\": \"hard|guidance\",\n  \"scope\": \"global|subgraph\",\n  \"affectedNodes\": [nodeRef]?\n}\n```\n\n**Codex treatment**: Hard constraints become validation rules in every execution prompt; guidance becomes advisory text.",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
