      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Decision\n\n**Purpose**: Recorded, timestamped choice that closes discussion or questions.\n\n**Distinct from discussion**: Discussion lives in markdown or Open Question nodes; Decision is the resolved state.\n\n**Canonical data shape**:\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"string\",\n  \"markdown\": \"string\",\n  \"rationale\": \"string\",\n  \"status\": \"pending|decided|superseded\",\n  \"decidedAt\": \"YYYY-MM-DD\",\n  \"supersededBy\": nodeRef?,\n  \"owner\": \"string?\"\n}\n```\n\n**Rules**: Can supersede older decisions (chain via supersededBy). Connects to Tasks (triggers), Constraints (sets), Open Questions (resolves).",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
