      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Open Question\n\n**Purpose**: Unresolved item that blocks clarity.\n\n**Distinct from risk/investigation**: Question = \"we don't know yet\"; risk = \"bad thing might happen\".\n\n**Canonical data shape**:\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"string\",\n  \"markdown\": \"string\",\n  \"owner\": \"string?\",\n  \"status\": \"open|investigating|resolved\",\n  \"resolutionPath\": nodeRef?,\n  \"prominence\": \"high|normal\"\n}\n```\n\n**Lifecycle**: Resolution converts it -> Decision (most common), Task, or closed Note. Unresolved questions auto-surface in Codex planning prompts.",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
