      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Task\n\n**Purpose**: Smallest atomic unit Codex can implement in one focused prompt cycle.\n\n**Canonical data shape**:\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"string\",\n  \"markdown\": \"string\",\n  \"status\": \"todo|in-progress|done|blocked\",\n  \"owner\": \"string?\",\n  \"priority\": \"high|medium|low\",\n  \"estimateHours\": number?,\n  \"acceptanceCriteria\": [nodeRef]\n}\n```\n\n**Rules**: Must be small enough for one-shot execution. Links to Goal (contributesTo), Dependencies, Acceptance Criteria, Risks.",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
