      ],
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Dependency\n\n**Primary representation**: Edge (with optional metadata: type = prereq|blocker|external).\n\n**Node form** (only when needed):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"string\",\n  \"markdown\": \"string\",\n  \"type\": \"prereq|blocker|external|resource\",\n  \"status\": \"open|resolved\",\n  \"externalId\": \"string?\"\n}\n```\n\n**Connection rules**: Simple cases = edge + label/metadata. Complex cases = Dependency node + multiple edges. (See Node Type vs Edge Type decision.)",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "_classBinding": {
