        }
      ],
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Acceptance Criteria\n\n**Purpose**: Verifiable checklist that proves a Task/Goal/Decision is complete.\n\n**Format**: Structured checklist (preferred) or Gherkin-style.\n\n**Attachment**: Primarily to Tasks; optionally to Goals or Decisions.\n\n**Canonical data shape**:\n```json\n{\n  \"items\": [\n    {\n      \"description\": \"string\",\n      \"type\": \"checkbox|test|metric\",\n      \"verified\": boolean\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**Verification intent**: Codex uses these directly in validation prompts; future auto-review agents will run against them.",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
