      ],
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Risk / Edge Case\n\n**Purpose**: Potential failure mode or unhandled scenario (kept combined for v1).\n\n**Canonical data shape**:\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"string\",\n  \"markdown\": \"string\",\n  \"severity\": \"low|medium|high|critical\",\n  \"likelihood\": \"low|medium|high\",\n  \"mitigationPlan\": \"string or nodeRef\",\n  \"status\": \"open|mitigated|accepted\",\n  \"linkedTo\": [nodeRef]\n}\n```\n\n**Escalation**: High-risk items auto-generate a Task or Decision. Edge cases become acceptance-criteria tests.",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "_classBinding": {
